SUMMARY:Little Explorers
DESCRIPTION:Thursday June 4 – Aug 69:30 – 10:30 am11:00 am – 12:00 pm \n\n\n\n$10 member / $12 nonmember (per child\, per class)Ages 2-4 \n\n\n\nEach child must be accompanied by their guardian. Siblings are welcome to attend but must be registered to participate. \n\n\n\nFamily Tree Membership and above required for member discount. \n\n\n\nOur youngest naturalists are invited to join us for hands-on nature exploration. This program is a perfect way for our Little Explorers to discover more about the natural world around them.  \n\n\n\nPlease come dressed for the outdoors\, including closed-toe shoes. A parent or guardian is required to attend program with children. \n\n\n\nSummer Children’s Program registration will open Tuesday\, February 3\, 2026 for Arboretum Members. Nonmember registration will open Tuesday\, February 10\, 2026. \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n9:30 am Classes\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 4 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 11 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 18 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 25 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJUly 2 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 9 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 16 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 23 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 30 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\naugust 6 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\n\n11:00 am Classes\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 4 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 11 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 18 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 25 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJUly 2 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 9 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 16 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 23 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 30 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\naugust 6 – 11:00 am\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPlease come dressed for the outdoors\, including closed-toe shoes. \n\n\n\n\nfaqs
