SUMMARY:Solstice Sip & Craft
DESCRIPTION:$37 member / $52 nonmemberAges 21+ \n\n\n\nCelebrate the longest day of the year by cultivating your creativity! Enjoy Saint Arnold Brewing Company beer while you make crafts and décor using natural materials. We’ll make seasonal wreaths\, ornaments\, beeswax candles\, and more. \n\n\n\nPlease dress for the weather and wear clothes you don’t mind getting messy. \n\n\n\n\nRegister Online
URL:https://houstonarboretum.org/event/solstice-sip-craft/
CATEGORIES:Adult Programs,Art & Photography
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://houstonarboretum.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Person-holding-beeswax-candles-Alina-Vilchenko.jpg
END:VEVENT
