UID:10001533-1782554400-1782561600@houstonarboretum.org
SUMMARY:Gardening for Bees
DESCRIPTION:$22 member / $37 nonmemberAges 12+\, minors must be accompanied by an adult \n\n\n\nSet the table for bees in your garden! Learn all about the best native plants for bees\, techniques to help bees survive the extremes of summer and winter\, and how to provide nesting space for these critical pollinators. \n\n\n\nPlease dress for the weather and wear walking shoes. \n\n\n\n\nregister online
URL:https://houstonarboretum.org/event/gardening-for-bees/
CATEGORIES:Adult Programs,Nature & Wildlife,Plants & Gardening
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://houstonarboretum.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Carpenter-Bee-Christine-Mansfield.jpg
END:VEVENT
