SUMMARY:Animal Tales
DESCRIPTION:Mondays\, June 1 – August 39:30 am and 10:30 am \n\n\n\n$5 member / $7 nonmember (per child\, per class)Ages 18 months to 3 years \n\n\n\nEach child must be accompanied by their guardian. Siblings are welcome to attend but must be registered to participate. \n\n\n\nFamily Tree Membership level and above required for member discount. \n\n\n\nJoin us for a weekly story time featuring some of our favorite animals! Each week we will read a nature-themed book\, observe biofacts and/or live animals\, and then venture out on the trails for a self-guided hike. \n\n\n\nSummer Children’s Program registration will open Tuesday\, February 3\, 2026 for Arboretum Members. Nonmember registration will open Tuesday\, February 10\, 2026. \n\n\n\n\n\n9:30 am Classes\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 1 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 8 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 15 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 22 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 29 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 6 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 13 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 20 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 27 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\naugust 3 – 9:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\n\n10:30 am Classes\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 1 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 8 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 15 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 22 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJune 29 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 6 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 13 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 20 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\nJuly 27 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\naugust 3 – 10:30 am\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPlease come dressed for the outdoors\, including closed-toe shoes.  \n\n\n\n\nfaqs
